    "text": "$$\n\\text{Ta có: } I = \\int_{-1}^{2} [x + 2f(x) - 3g(x)]dx = \\frac{x^2}{2} \\Big|_{-1}^{2} + 2\\int_{-1}^{2} f(x)dx - 3\\int_{-1}^{2} g(x)dx = \\frac{3}{2} + 2 \\cdot 2 - 3 \\cdot (-1) = \\frac{17}{2}.\n$$"
